<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head lang="en">
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title></title>
<style>


*{
	box-sizing:border-box;
}
img{
			display:inline-block;
			max-width:100%;
			margin:0;
			
		}
#main{
	position:relative;
	width:100%;
}

.part_right{
	width:80%;
	position:absolute;
	right:0;
	top:0;
}
.part_right>div{
border:1px solid red;
width:100%;
/*height:300px;*/
border:20px solid black;
}

.part_right>div>img{

width:100%;
margin:0 auto;
display:inline-block;
}
h2{
	font-size:50px;
	padding-left:20px;
}


.part_left{
	width:20%;
	/*
	position:fixed;
	left:0;
	top:0;
	overflow:auto;
*/
	position:   fixed;
        top:        0;
        bottom:     0;
        left:       0;
        right:      0;
        border:     1px solid black;
        overflow:   hidden;
        background: white;
}
.a_box{
	
	word-wrap: break-word;
	word-break: break-all;
	overflow:auto;

    max-height: 98%;      /*这个词是重点*/
	
}
.a_group{
	
}
.a_group>a{
	display:block;
	margin:10px 0;
}
pre{
		width:100%；
		padding:0;
		white-space: pre-wrap;
		word-wrap: break-word;
		}

h3{
	margin:0!important;
	padding:0!important;
}
h3,b{
color:red;
}
.imp{
border:1px solid red;
padding:20px;
margin:20px;
}
</style>
<script src="jquery-1.9.1.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
<div id="main">
<div class="part_left">
<h1>angular_day01</h1>
	<div class="a_box">
		<div class="a_group">
			<a href="#d1">1.设备宽度在区间范围内执行样式</a>
			<a href="#d2">2.设备宽度在区间范围内执行css</a>
			<a href="#d3">3.not(了解)</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="part_right">
<div>
	<h2 id="d1">1.设备宽度在区间范围内执行样式</h2>
	<pre>
	例1：
		@media screen and (min-device-width:992px){
			div {display:none;}
		}
	例2：
		@media screen and (min-device-width:768px) and (max-device-width:991px){
			body {background-color:#f5f5f5;}
		}
	
<pre class="imp">
<h3>提醒！！！</h3>
1.一般做媒体查询:
	都用<b>max-device-width</b>【依据设备大小】，不用max-width【依据浏览器大小】
2.尺寸设置【关键数字:768,992,1200】
	 X > <b>992</b>               -- > pc  
	 <b>768</b> < X < <b>991</b>        -- > pad  
	 X < <b>767</b>             -- > 手机
</pre>

	</pre>
</div>
<div>
	<h2 id="d2">2.设备宽度在区间范围内执行css</h2>
	<pre>
	例1：
		< link rel="stylesheet" media="screen and (min-device-width:992px)" href="demo.css" / >
	例2：
		< link rel="stylesheet" media="(min-device-width:768px) and (max-device-width:991px)" href="demo.css" / >
<pre class="imp">
<h3>提醒！！！</h3>
1.一般做媒体查询:
	都用<b>max-device-width</b>【依据设备大小】，不用max-width【依据浏览器大小】
2.尺寸设置【关键数字:768,992,1200】
	 X > <b>992</b>               -- > pc  
	 <b>768</b> < X < <b>991</b>        -- > pad  
	 X < <b>767</b>             -- > 手机
</pre>
	</pre>
</div>
<div>
	<h2 id="d3">3.宽度大于1200px的执行该样式（了解）</h2>
	<pre>
		@media not print and (max-width: 1200px){
			div {display:none;}
		}
	</pre>
</div>

</div>
</div>
</body>

</html>